name: CNN
text:
Amazon CEO Jeff Bezos is opening the doors of his first preschool, the Bezos Academy.

It's the first location of a network of tuition-free preschools serving children in underserved communities spearheaded by Bezos' philanthropic arm, Day One Fund. https://t.co/Rnrrvb7qNi

name: CNN
text: The Amazon-owned home security company Ring has unveiled a prototype for a drone meant to fly around in your house called the Ring Always Home Cam. It's set to release in 2021. https://t.co/RFgXbWvnrc https://t.co/nPIImCDZK1

name: CNN
text: BREAKING: A federal judge blocks -- for now -- a US government ban on downloads of TikTok just hours before the policy was set to take effect https://t.co/4gJM1Zkmki

name: CNN
text: Three railroad workers were suspended for building a man cave under Grand Central Terminal in New York. The room included a wall-mounted TV and streaming device, futon, air mattress, refrigerator and microwave, Metropolitan Transportation Authority says. https://t.co/YoK1yPGL1A

name: CNN
text: Volkswagen has unveiled its first electric SUV, the ID.4. VW calls the ID.4 its first long-range electric vehicle for the US market, and says it's an important part of the brand's overall move toward electric vehicles. https://t.co/MAFtiAB4rU https://t.co/w6lLwMeYIn

name: CNN
text: An ordinary workday quickly turned into a rescue mission after a bridge inspector spotted a stranded dog 120 feet above the Mississippi River https://t.co/JQ3qBGiyBf
